Game Notes:

Get ready to conquer the Wild West on the train! Will design and build a structure with an elaborated arrangements, hire a sensible team 
and go to the spirited journey through America! With the mind, use resources, organizing passenger and freight transportation; solve problems the 
way you want.

or higher 
DirectX: Version 9.0c 
Storage: 1500 MB available space 
Sound Card: DirectX 9.0c Compatible Sound 
Card with Latest Drivers
Mouse, Keyboard

1. Download
2. Install the game
3. Run the game as administrator
4. Have fun
